import React from "react";
import {Text, View, Button } from "react-native";
function Events () {
    return (
    <View style={styles.main}>
    <View style={styles.event}>
      <View style={styles.date}>
        <Text style={styles.dateText}>11TH NOV</Text>
      </View>
      <View style={styles.description}>
        <Text style={styles.text}>
          <Text>Sunday Supper Club</Text>
          <Text>
            A culinary event with foods from all over the world. This is a
            weekly club you can join for a small fee. Learn to cook something
            delicious and beautiful
          </Text>
        </Text>
      </View>
      <View style={styles.button}>
        <Button style={styles.text} title="+ Event Details" />
      </View>
      <View style={styles.address}>
        <Text style={styles.text}>
          <Text>16:00 - 19:00</Text>
          <Text>144 W Elm St.Chicago, II, 60610, USA</Text>
        </Text>
      </View>
    </View>
    <Separator />
  </View>
    )
}

export default Events;
